Join @planwithlaur tonight on @qvc at 6:15PM during At Home With Pat to snag this bundle! Until then you can check out this replay for a sneak peek! 

Shop the bundle: https://qvc.co/ErinCondrenWSVFB

#erincondren #erincondrenacademicplanner

You are exactly right to feel a lot right now It does not mean you're weak- it means you're strong enough to be paying attention. Be gentle with you, please.'.

node.text: We needed this today. Thanks, @glennondoyle. #MotivationalMonday

node.text: GIVEAWAY ALERT! We are celebrating #backtoschool and #teachers with @modcloth! Make sure you are following both @erincondren and @modcloth and tag a friend in the comments for your chance to win a $150 EC gift card and a $150 gift card to the ModCloth to win! Entries are unlimited. #giveaway ends 8/27/21. Winners will be contacted privately via DM.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Erin Condren Design on August 20, 2021.

node.text: There's still time to grab all of your favorite Back To School goodies before returning to the classroom or office! 📸: @megansgotplans Shop our curated back to school collection today.

node.text: Anyone else OBSESSED with planny packs? 🙋 You've got to have one to match every cover right? Tell us your favorite planny pack design in the comments.

node.text: TODAY IS THE LAST DAY OF OUR WAREHOUSE SALE! Don't miss our final FLASH DEAL- enjoy $2 sticker sheets!
